title: Down on Trended Knee 6/19: Ansel Elgort, Tulsa, Gavin Newson, Juneteenth
itunes:title: Down on Trended Knee 6/19: Ansel Elgort, Tulsa, Gavin Newson, Juneteenth
description:
On this edition of Down on Trended Knee Miles and Laci discuss Ansel Elgort being accused of raping a 17-year old girl in 2014, Trump is about to host a rally in Tulsa, Gavin Newsom has mandated mask wearing in the state of California, and today is Juneteenth - a celebration of the day slaves were freed in Texas after the Civil War.
